				   left edge of a group box</para>
                </entry>
                <entry>
                  <para>14; if the
				   group box is left-aligned, controls are 24 from the left edge of the dialog
				   box or property page</para>
                </entry>
              </row>
              <row>
                <entry>
                  <para>Last
				   control in a group box</para>
                </entry>
